%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109084516%2Cimgsize-54576.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fenglish%2Fpatrick-j-adams-and-sarah-rafferty-team-up-for-suits-rewatch-podcast-read-deets%2Farticleshow%2F109084430.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109084430.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPatrick%20J%20Adams%20and%20Sarah%20Rafferty%20host%20SiriusXM%20podcast%2C%20analyzing%20'Suits'%20episodes%20with%20insider%20details%20on%20characters%20Mike%20Ross%2C%20Donna%20Paulsen%2C%20Harvey%20Specter%2C%20and%20streaming%20records.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Madhya%20Pradesh%20Court's%20Unique%20Order%20On%20Breakup%20After%20A%20Live-In%20Relationship%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20has%20taken%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%20recognizing%20the%20rights%20of%20women%20in%20live-in%20relationships%20by%20ruling%20that%20a%20woman%20living%20with%20a%20man%20for%20a%20considerable%20period%20is%20entitled%20to%20maintenance%20upon%20separation%2C%20even%20if%20they%20are%20not%20legally%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20came%20as%20a%20response%20to%20a%20petitioner%20who%20challenged%20a%20trial%20court%20order%20requiring%20him%20to%20pay%20a%20monthly%20allowance%20of%20Rs%201%2C500%20to%20a%20woman%20with%20whom%20he%20had%20been%20in%20a%20live-in%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20progressive%20move%2C%20the%20judges%20emphasized%20that%20maintenance%20cannot%20be%20denied%20if%20there%20is%20evidence%20of%20cohabitation%20between%20the%20couple.%20The%20High%20Court%20cited%20the%20trial%20court's%20finding%2C%20which%20concluded%20that%20the%20man%20and%20woman%20had%20been%20living%20as%20husband%20and%20wife.%20Additionally%2C%20considering%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20child%20within%20the%20relationship%2C%20the%20court%20affirmed%20the%20woman's%20entitlement%20to%20maintenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20landmark%20decision%20underscores%20the%20evolving%20legal%20landscape%20regarding%20live-in%20relationships%20in%20India.%20It%20signifies%20a%20departure%20from%20traditional%20norms%20and%20a%20recognition%20of%20the%20rights%20and%20vulnerabilities%20of%20women%20in%20such%20partnerships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Uttarakhand%20brought%20a%20uniform%20civil%20code%20to%20provide%20a%20legal%20framework%20for%20uniform%20marriage%2C%20divorce%2C%20land%2C%20property%2C%20and%20inheritance%20laws%20for%20all%20citizens.%20One%20of%20the%20sections%20of%20the%20bill%20made%20registration%20of%20live-in%20relationships%20mandatory.%20It%20also%20states%20that%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20couple%20will%20be%20notified%20if%20they%20are%20adults%20under%20the%20age%20of%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712390340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fgdieuj5k_couple-generic_625x300_06_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-courts-unique-order-on-breakup-after-a-live-in-relationship-5386379%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20has%20taken%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%20recognizing%20the%20rights%20of%20women%20in%20live-in%20relationships%20by%20ruling%20that%20a%20woman%20living%20with%20a%20man%20for%20a%20considerable%20period%20is%20entitled%20to%20maintenance%20upon%20separation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-courts-unique-order-on-breakup-after-a-live-in-relationship-5386379%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findi