20time%20since%202020%20the%20arch-rival%20billionaires%20have%20held%20those%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20who%20ranked%20first%20on%20the%20Bloomberg%20Billionaires%20Index%20as%20recently%20as%20early%20March%2C%20fell%20to%20fourth%20after%20Reuters%20reported%20Tesla%20Inc.%20had%20canceled%20plans%20for%20a%20less-expensive%20car%2C%20sending%20shares%20lower.%20(Musk%20denied%20the%20report.)%20That%20followed%20news%20earlier%20in%20the%20week%20that%20Tesla's%20vehicle%20deliveries%20fell%20in%20the%20three%20months%20through%20March%2C%20their%20first%20year-over-year%20decline%20since%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20Covid%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk's%20wealth%20has%20shrunk%20by%20%2448.4%20billion%20this%20year%2C%20while%20Zuckerberg%20has%20added%20%2458.9%20billion%20to%20his%20fortune%20as%20Meta%20Platforms%20Inc.%20climbs%20to%20fresh%20highs%2C%20including%20a%20new%20record%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20first%20time%20Zuckerberg%20has%20broken%20into%20the%20top%20three%20on%20Bloomberg's%20ranking%20of%20the%20richest%20people%20since%20Nov.%2016%2C%202020%2C%20when%20he%20was%20worth%20%24105.6%20billion%20and%20Musk's%20fortune%20was%20%24102.1%20billion.%20Musk%20now%20has%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%24180.6%20billion%3B%20Zuckerberg's%20is%20%24186.9%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reversal%20of%20the%20wealth%20gap%20between%20Musk%20and%20Zuckerberg%2C%20which%20was%20as%20big%20as%20%24215%20billion%20in%20November%202021%2C%20illustrates%20how%20once-hot%20electric%20vehicle%20stocks%20have%20been%20usurped%20by%20big%20tech%2C%20and%20particularly%20anything%20involving%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20shares%20have%20fallen%2034%25%20this%20year%2C%20making%20it%20the%20worst%20performer%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20Index.%20It's%20been%20battered%20by%20a%20global%20slowdown%20in%20EV%20demand%2C%20growing%20competition%20in%20China%20and%20production%20problems%20in%20Germany.%20Meta%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20surged%2049%25%20thanks%20to%20strong%20quarterly%20earnings%20and%20excitement%20about%20the%20company's%20AI%20initiatives.%20It's%20the%20fifth-best%20performer%20on%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20billionaires'%20rivalry%20extends%20beyond%20their%20wealth%3A%20Musk%20and%20Zuckerberg%20have%20been%20engaged%20in%20an%20ongoing%20public%20spat%20that%20intensified%20when%20Meta%20launched%20Threads%2C%20a%20social-media%20platform%20that%20competes%20with%20Musk's%20X.%20The%20two%20even%20traded%20barbs%20last%20year%20about%20a%20possible%20cage%20fight.%20Musk%2C%2052%2C%20recently%20revived%20the%20idea%20on%20X%2C%20saying%20he%20would%20fight%20Zuckerberg%2C%2039%2C%20%26quot%3Banywhere%2C%20anytime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk's%20net%20worth%20could%20take%20a%20further%20hit%20after%20his%20%2455%20billion%20Tesla%20pay%20package%20was%20struck%20down%20by%20a%20Delaware%20judge.%20The%20Bloomberg%20Billionaires%20Index%20continues%20to%20use%20the%20options%20from%20that%20pay%20package%2C%20which%20are%20one%20of%20Musk's%20largest%20assets%2C%20in%20its%20calculations%20of%20his%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBernard%20Arnault%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20luxury%20giant%20LVMH%20Moet%20Hennessy%20Louis%20Vuitton%2C%20and%20Amazon.com%20Inc.%20founder%20Jeff%20Bezos%20hold%20the%20first%20two%20spots%20on%20Bloomberg's%20wealth%20ranking%20with%20fortunes%20of%20%24223.4%20billion%20and%20%24207.3%20billion%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712388960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F86jsk76g_mark-zuckerberg-bloomberg_625x300_02_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmark-zuckerberg-becomes-richer-