%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftotal-solar-eclipse-90-of-us-airbnbs-booked-to-view-cosmic-spectacle%2Famp_articleshow%2F109083522.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftotal-solar-eclipse-90-of-us-airbnbs-booked-to-view-cosmic-spectacle%2Famp_articleshow%2F109083522.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'NIA%20officials%20attacked%20villagers%20in%20Bengal%2C%20not%20other%20way%20round'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712387549000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109083579%2Cimgsize-754707.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwhy-went-at-midnight-mamata-questions-nias-probe-timing-after-attack-on-agency%2Farticleshow%2F109083030.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20NIA's%20probe%20into%20the%20Medinipur%20blast%20case.%20The%20NIA%20team%2C%20en%20route%20to%20Kolkata%2C%20was%20attacked%20in%20Bhupatinagar.%20Banerjee%20criticized%20the%20midnight%20raid%2C%20stating%20that%20locals%20reacted%20as%20they%20would%20to%20any%20stranger%20visiting%20at%20that%20hour.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BLoyalty%20Should%20Be%20With...%26quot%3B%3A%20Chief%20Justice%20To%20Judges%20Ahead%20Of%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhile%20every%20Indian%20is%20likely%20to%20harbor%20a%20political%20ideology%20or%20inclination%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20emphasized%20today%20that%20the%20loyalty%20of%20lawyers%20and%20judges%20should%20be%20directed%20towards%20the%20Constitution.%20Making%20the%20remarks%20just%20days%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20begin%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20stressed%20the%20need%20for%20judges%20to%20be%20non-partisan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20vibrant%20and%20argumentative%20democracy%20like%20ours%2C%20most%20individuals%20have%20a%20political%20ideology%20or%20inclination.%20Aristotle%20said%20human%20beings%20are%20political%20animals%2C%20and%20lawyers%20are%20no%20exception.%20However%2C%20for%20members%20of%20the%20bar%20one's%20highest%20loyalty%20should%20not%20lie%20with%20partisan%20interests%20but%20with%20the%20court%20and%20the%20constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%20at%20the%20centenary%20year%20celebration%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20Bar%20Association%20of%20Nagpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20reiterated%20that%20the%20judiciary%20has%20consistently%20risen%20to%20the%20occasion%20to%20%26quot%3Bassert%20its%20independence%20and%20non-partisanship%2C%20ensuring%20the%20separation%20of%20powers%20from%20the%20executive%2C%20the%20legislature%2C%20and%20vested%20political%20interests.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20not%20forget%2C%20however%2C%20that%20there%20is%20a%20close%20link%20between%20the%20independence%20of%20the%20judiciary%20and%20the%20independence%20of%20the%20bar%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CJI%20emphasized.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20underscored%20that%20an%20independent%20bar%20serves%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmoral%20bulwark%20to%20safeguard%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20constitutional%20governance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20said%20the%20judgments%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20constitutional%20benches%20represent%20the%20culmination%20of%20rigorous%20proceedings%2C%20thorough%20legal%20analysis%2C%20and%20a%20commitment%20to%20constitutional%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20a%20judgment%20is%20pronounced%2C%20it%20becomes%20public%20property.%20As%20an%20institution%2C%20we%20have%20broad%20shoulders.%20We%20are%20prepared%20to%20receive%20both%20praise%20and%20criticism...%20commendations%20and%20critiques%2C%20whether%20through%20journalistic%20pieces%2C%20political%20commentary%2C%20or%20on%20social%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20members%20and%20office-bearers%20of%20bar%20associations%2C%20lawyers%20must%20maintain%20a%20distinction%20from%20laypersons%20when%20reacting%20to%20court%20judgments%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20late%2C%20I%20have%20been%20very%20disturbed%20by%20the%20tendency%20of%20members%20of%20bar%20associations%20to%20comment%20on%20cases%20that%20are%20pending%20and%20on%20judgments.%20You%20are%20first%20and%20foremost%20officers%20of%20the%20court%2C%20and%20the%20truth%20and%20dignity%20of%20our%20legal%20discourse%20is%20in%20your%20hands%2C%26quot%3B%20DY%20Chandrachud%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712387160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fogfpl31o_dy-chandrachud_625x300_06_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhave-political-ideology-but-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-message-for-judges-lawyers-on-constitution-elections-5386018%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20every%20Indian%20is%20likely%20to%20harbor%20a%20political%20ideology%20or%20inclination%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20emphasized%20today%20that%20the%20loyalty%20of%20lawyers%20and%20judges%20should%20be%20directed%20towards%20the%20Constitution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhave-political-ideology-but-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-message-for-judges-lawyers-on-constitution-elections-5386018%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhave-political-ideology-but-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-message-for-judges-lawyers-on-constitution-elections-5386018%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhave-political-ideology-but-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-message-for-judges-lawyers-on