20Manna%20in%20Naruabilla%20village%20of%20East%20Medinipur%20district.%20Rajkumar%20Manna%2C%20along%20with%20Biswajit%20Gayen%20and%20Buddhadeb%20Manna%2C%20died%20in%20the%20blast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Police%20registered%20a%20an%20FIR%20on%20December%203%2C%202022.%20However%2C%20the%20Explosive%20Substances%20Act%20was%20not%20initially%20applied%20in%20the%20case.%20Subsequently%2C%20a%20writ%20petition%20was%20filed%20at%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%2C%20urging%20the%20inclusion%20of%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20Act%20and%20the%20transfer%20of%20the%20case%20to%20the%20NIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20incident%2C%20a%20large%20police%20contingent%20was%20dispatched%20to%20the%20scene%20to%20bring%20the%20situation%20under%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20president%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20alleged%20that%20the%20NIA%20was%20working%20for%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20did%20they%20raid%20at%20midnight%3F%20Did%20they%20have%20police%20permission%3F%20Locals%20reacted%20in%20the%20way%20they%20would%20have%20if%20any%20other%20stranger%20had%20visited%20the%20place%20at%20midnight.%20Why%20are%20they%20arresting%20people%20right%20before%20the%20elections%3F%20What%20does%20the%20BJP%20think%2C%20that%20they%20will%20arrest%20every%20booth%20agent%3F%20What%20right%20does%20NIA%20have%3F%20They%20are%20doing%20all%20these%20to%20support%20the%20BJP.%20We%20call%20upon%20the%20entire%20world%20to%20fight%20against%20this%20BJP's%20dirty%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20accused%20NIA%20personnel%20of%20assaulting%20residents%20in%20Bhupatinagar%20rather%20than%20the%20villagers%20initiating%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712381100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fk1u84rso_nia-team-attacked-in-east-midnapo