rps%20has%20said%20that%20seven%20Iranian%20military%20advisers%20died%20in%20the%20strike%2C%20including%20Mohammad%20Reza%20Zahedi%2C%20a%20senior%20commander%20in%20its%20Quds%20Force%2C%20which%20is%20an%20elite%20foreign%20espionage%20and%20paramilitary%20arm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20has%20said%20it%20reserves%20the%20right%20%26quot%3Bto%20take%20a%20decisive%20response%26quot%3B%20and%20will%20deliver%20a%20%26quot%3Bslap%26quot%3B%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Is%20US%20On%20High%20Alert%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20escalation%20of%20the%20Iran-Israel%20conflict%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20dialled%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20and%20assured%20him%20of%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20teams%20have%20been%20in%20regular%20and%20continuous%20contact%20since%20then.%20The%20United%20States%20fully%20supports%20the%20defense%20of%20Israel%20against%20threats%20from%20Iran%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20Biden%20administration%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20just%20hours%20after%20the%20Biden%20call%20became%20public%2C%20Iran%20issued%20a%20statement%20warning%20the%20US%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20written%20message%20to%20Washington%2C%20Iran%20%26quot%3Bwarned%20the%20US%20not%20to%20get%20dragged%20into%20Netanyahu's%20trap%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohammad%20Jamshidi%2C%20the%20Iranian%20president's%20deputy%20chief%20of%20staff%20for%20political%20affairs%2C%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20referring%20to%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu.%20The%20US%20should%20%26quot%3Bstep%20aside%20so%20that%20you%20don't%20get%20hit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20An%20All-Out%20War%20Between%20Israel%20And%20Iran%20A%20Possibility%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20specter%20of%20all-out%20war%20looms%20large%2C%20particularly%20concerning%20Iran's%20nuclear%20program.%20Despite%20Iran's%20claims%20of%20