%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20world%2C%20at%20least%2064%20countries%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20are%20expected%20to%20hold%20national%20elections.%20These%20countries%20collectively%20account%20for%20approximately%2049%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20global%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Microsoft's%20threat%20intelligence%20team%2C%20Chinese%20state-backed%20cyber%20groups%2C%20along%20with%20involvement%20from%20North%20Korea%2C%20are%20expected%20to%20target%20several%20elections%20scheduled%20for%202024.%20Microsoft%20said%20that%20China%20will%20likely%20deploy%20AI-generated%20content%20via%20social%20media%20to%20sway%20public%20opinion%20in%20favour%20of%20their%20interests%20during%20these%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20major%20elections%20taking%20place%20around%20the%20world%20this%20year%2C%20particularly%20in%20India%2C%20South%20Korea%20and%20the%20United%20States%2C%20we%20assess%20that%20China%20will%2C%20at%20a%20minimum%2C%20create%20and%20amplify%20AI-generated%20content%20to%20benefit%20its%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20Microsoft%20said%20in%20its%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThreat%20Of%20AI%20In%20Elections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20threat%20posed%20by%20political%20advertisements%20employing%20AI%20technology%20to%20produce%20deceptive%20and%20false%20content%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bdeepfakes%26quot%3B%20or%20fabricating%20events%20that%20never%20took%20place%2C%20is%20significant%20in%20a%20crucial%20poll%20year.%20Such%20tactics%20aim%20to%20mislead%20the%20public%20regarding%20candidates'%20statements%2C%20stances%20on%20various%20issues%2C%20and%20even%20the%20authenticity%20of%20certain%20events.%20If%20allowed%20to%20go%20unchecked%2C%20these%20manipulative%20attempts%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20undermine%20voters'%20ability%20to%20make%20well-informed%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20immediate%20impact%20of%20AI-generated%20content%20remains%20relatively%20low%2C%20Microsoft%20warned%20that%20China's%20increasing%20experimentation%20with%20this%20technology%20could%20potentially%20become%20more%20effective%20over%20time.%20The%20tech%20giant%20noted%20that%20China's%20previous%20attempt%20to%20influence%20Taiwan's%20election%20involved%20the%20dissemination%20of%20AI-generated%20disinformation%2C%20marking%20the%20first%20instance%20of%20a%20state-backed%20entity%20utilising%20such%20tactics%20in%20a%20foreign%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fo6v1d3vg_china-taiwan_625x300_23_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Taiwanese%20election%2C%20a%20Beijing-backed%20group%20known%20as%20Storm%201376%2C%20or%20Spamouflage%2C%20was%20notably%20active%2C%20Microsoft%20said.%20This%20group%20circulated%20AI-generated%20content%2C%20including%20fake%20audio%20endorsements%20and%20memes%2C%20aimed%20at%20discrediting%20certain%20candidates%20and%20influencing%20voter%20perceptions.%20The%20use%20of%20AI-generated%20TV%20news%20anchors%2C%20is%20a%20tactic%20also%20employed%20by%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStorm-1376%20has%20promoted%20a%20series%20of%20AI-generated%20memes%20of%20Taiwan's%20then-Democratic%20Progressive%20Party%20(DPP)%20presidential%20candidate%20William%20Lai%2C%20and%20other%20Taiwanese%20officials%20as%20well%20as%20Chinese%20dissidents%20around%20the%20world.%20These%20have%20included%20an%20increasing%20use%20of%20AI-generated%20TV%20news%20anchors%20that%20Storm-1376%20has%20deployed%20since%20at%20least%20February%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20Microsoft%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20Influence%20In%20US%20Affairs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20pointed%20out%20that%20Chinese%20groups%20continue%20to%20conduct%20influence%20campaigns%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20leveraging%20social%20media%20platforms%20to%20pose%20divisive%20questions%20and%20gather%20intelligence%20on%20key%20voting%20demographics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20an%20increased%20use%20of%20Chinese%20AI-generated%20content%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20attempting%20to%20influence%20and%20sow%20division%20in%20the%20US%20and%20elsewhere%20on%20a%20range%20of%20topics%20including%20the%20train%20derailment%20in%20Kentucky%20in%20November%202023%2C%20the%20Maui%20wildfires%20in%20August%202023%2C%20the%20disposal%20of%20Japanese%20nuclear%20wastewater%2C%20drug%20use%20in%20the%20US%20as%20well%20as%20immigration%20policies%20and%20racial%20tensions%20in%20the%20country.%20There%20is%20little%20evidence%20these%20efforts%20have%20been%20successful%20in%20swaying%20opinion%2C%26quot%3B%20Microsoft%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F2d31g3cg_potus-joe-biden_625x300_19_December_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20AI%20in%20US%20election%20campaigns%20is%20not%20new.%20In%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%202024%20New%20Hampshire%20Democratic%20primaries%2C%20an%20AI-generated%20phone%20call%20mimicked%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20voice%2C%20advising%20voters%20against%20participating%20in%20the%20polling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20call%20falsely%20insinuated%20that%20voters%20should%20withhold%20their%20votes%20for%20the%20general%20election%20in%20November%20instead.%20Upon%20hearing%20this%20message%2C%20the%20average%20voter%20could%20easily%20have%20been%20misled%20into%20believing%20that%20President%20Biden%20himself%20had%20endorsed%20this%20directive%2C%20potentially%20leading%20to%20their%20disenfranchisement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20there