20there%20were%20very%20less%20friction%20as%20less%20as%20controversy%20surrounding%20the%20decision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20got%20to%20have%20a%20succession%20plan%20and%20you've%20seen%20the%20same%20thing%20with%20CSK%20last%20season%20didn't%20we%2C%20when%20Jaddu%20came%20into%20captaincy%20and%20it%20didn't%20quite%20work%20for%20them%20so%20maybe%20there%20is%20an%20opportunity%20to%20reassess%2C%20there%20are%20some%20concerns%20in%20and%20around%20Hardik's%20leadership%20but%20I%20think%20it's%20grossly%20unfair%20to%20look%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20season%20which%20is%20notoriously%20slow%20for%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20and%20judge%20one%20of%20the%20iconic%20cricketers%20in%20India%20and%20will%20be%20for%20a%20long%20time%20to%20come%20as%20well%2C%20subject%20to%20his%20own%20fitness%20which%20is%20always%20vulnerable%20being%20an%20all-rounder%20as%20he%20is.%20But%20it's%20grossly%20unfair%20to%20misjudge%20his%20performances%20so%20far%2C%20and%20the%20team's%20performances%20and%20then%20speculate%20around%20what%20is%20and%20what%20isn't%20happening%20inside%20that%20changing%20room%20which%20we%20don't%20know%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712376480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Faenb504o_hardik-pandya-rohit-sharma-mi_625x300_20_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fensure-that-rohit-sharma-is-on-board-australia-great-blasts-mumbai-indians-succession-plan-5381690%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20controversy%20surrounding%20Hardik%20Pandya%20replacing%20Rohit%20Sharma%20as%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20skipper%20has%20been%20dominating%20headlines%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20IPL%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A75%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHugging%20In%20Delhi%2C%20Begging%20In%20Kerala%26quot%3B%3A%20Smriti%20Irani%20On%20Congress-Left%20Sitch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Smriti%20Irani%20took%20a%20jibe%20at%20the%20Congress%20over%20its%20situation%20in%20Kerala%2C%20where%2C%20despite%20being%20partners%20in%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20has%20fielded%20Annie%20Raja%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20Wayanad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Irani%20on%20Friday%20said%20that%20on%20one%20side%2C%20the%20Left%20parties%20are%20asking%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20go%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20contest%2C%20while%20on%20the%20other%20side%2C%20the%20same%20Left%20members%20hugged%20the%20Congress%20leader%20during%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20INDI%20Alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20interaction%20with%20businessmen%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20condition%20of%20the%20opposition%20is%20that%20they%20are%20fighting%20in%20Wayanad.%20Left%20parties%20are%20saying%2C%20Why%20does%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20not%20go%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20contest.%20But%20when%20the%20same%20Left%20goes%20to%20Delhi%20for%20an%20INDI%20Alliance%20meeting%2C%20they%20hug%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20situation%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYesterday%20I%20said%20in%20Kerala%2C%20%3Cem%3E'Delhi%20mein%20hugging%2C%20Kerala%20mein%20begging.'%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20situation%20through%20which%20the%20Congress%20is%20going%20in%20Karnataka%20is%2C%20%3Cem%3E'Delhi%20mein%20hugging%2C%20Kerala%20mein%20begging%2C%20Karnataka%20mein%20thugging%3C%2Fem%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmriti%20Irani%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20former%20actress%2C%20requested%20that%20the%20women%20cast%20their%20votes%20in%20huge%20numbers%20and%20said%20that%20casting%20votes%20is%20not%20a%20game%20of%20any%20TV%20serial%3B%20instead%2C%20it's%20a%20heavy%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20request%20all%20the%20women%20that%20if%20we%20want%20everyone%20to%20take%20women%20seriously%20in%20politics%2C%20then%20we%20have%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20important%20political%20issues.%20'Saas-Bahu'%20serials%20are%20very%20far%20from%20the%20realities%20of%20life.%20Women%20who%20understand%20this%20can%20have%20a%20successful%20social%20and%20political%20life.%20The%20Gandhi%20family%20looted%20the%20country%20by%20clicking%20pictures%20and%20smiling.%20Casting%20your%20vote%20is%20a%20heavy%20responsibility%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20game%20of%20any%20TV%20serial%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnie%20Raja%20on%20Wednesday%20filed%20her%20nomination%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20Wayanad.%20The%20CPI%20is%20a%20partner%20of%20the%20ruling%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)-led%20Left%20Democratic%20Front%20in%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20CPI%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20partners%20in%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20the%20two%20parties%20are%20fierce%20contenders%20in%20Kerala%20with%20both%20parties%20pitting%20their%20strongest%20candidates%20against%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20which%20is%20leaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20establish%20its%20complete%20dominance%20in%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20has%20fielded%20Kerala%20State%20President%20K%20Surendran%20as%20a%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20candidate%20from%20the%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%2C%20one%20of%20the%20few%20states%20where%20the%20Congress%20still%20has%20a%20strong%20presence%2C%20sends%2020%20parliamentarians%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20won%20from%20Wayanad%20with%20a%20huge%20margin%20of%20over%204.31%20lakh%20votes%3B%20the%20highest%20margin%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20Kerala.%20He%20secured%2064.94%20per%20cent%20vote%20share%20defeating%20LDF%20candidate%20PP%20Suneer.%20The%20NDA%20had%20fielded%20BDJ(S)%20leader%20Tushar%20Vellapally%20who%20secured%20just%20around%2078%2C000%20votes%20which%20accounted%20for%20a%20mere%207.25%20per%20cent%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress-led%20United%20Democratic%20Front%20(UDF)%20won%2019%20out%20of%2020%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20While%20the%20Congress%20won%2015%20seats%2C%20its%20allies%20Indian%20Union%20Muslim%20League%20won%20two%20seats%2C%20the%20Revolutionary%20Socialist%20Party%20won%20one%20and%20the%20Kerala%20Congress%20(M)%20won%20one%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20won%20one%20seat%20in%20Alappuzha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20the%20South%20Indian%20state%20across%20all%2020%20seats%20is%20scheduled%20for%20April%2026%2C%20while%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20take%20place%20on%20June%204.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712376420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fgckdhq94_rahul-gandhi-pinarayi-vijayan-ani_625x300_06_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhugging-in-delhi-begging-in-kerala-smriti-irani-on-congress-left-sitch-5385154%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Smriti%20Irani%20took%20a%20jibe%20at%20the%20Congress%20over%20its%20situation%20in%20Kerala%2C%20where%2C%20despite%20being%20partners%20in%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20has%20fielded%20Annie%20Raja%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20Wayanad.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhugging-in-delhi-begging-in-kerala-smriti-irani-on-congress-left-sitch-5385154%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.amppro