e%20assassin%20Elektra%20Natchios%20in%20the%202003%20superhero%20movie%20%26quot%3BDaredevil%26quot%3B%20and%20her%20own%20spin-off%20movie%20%26quot%3BElektra%26quot%3B%20two%20years%20later.%20This%20led%20to%20a%20highly%20publicized%20marriage%20with%20her%20%26quot%3BDaredevil%26quot%3B%20costar%2C%20Ben%20Affleck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221074%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22elektra%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ad60aec7708e93234205174%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22710%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJennifer%20Garner%20as%20Elektra%20Natchios.%3Cp%3E20th%20Century%20Fox%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20that%20is%20over%20now.%20Garner%20is%20no%20longer%20in%20wigs%20beating%20up%20bad%20guys%2C%20nor%20is%20she%20married%20to%20Affleck%20(they%20divorced%20in%202018%20and%20have%20three%20kids).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20ensuing%20years%2C%20Garner%20made%20a%20major%20pivot%20to%20family-friendly%20content%2C%20and%20it's%20led%20to%20the%20kind%20of%20fame%20only%20a%20few%20can%20capture%3A%20she's%20become%20America's%20Mom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Tom%20Hanks%2C%20whose%20career%20choices%20made%20him%20so%20beloved%20by%20audiences%20that%20he%20became%20known%20as%20America's%20Dad%20to%20Gen%20Xers%2C%20Garner%20is%20becoming%20%26quot%3BMom%26quot%3B%20for%20Millenials.%20And%20you%20can%20thank%20Netflix%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20Garner%20has%20shown%20up%20in%20highly-watched%20family-friendly%20Netflix%20original%20movies%20%E2%80%94%202021's%20%26quot%3BYes%20Day%2C%26quot%3B%202022's%20%26quot%3BThe%20Adam%20Project%2C%26quot%3B%202023's%20%26quot%3BFamily%20Switch%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2024%2F04%2Fjennifer-garner-to-star-mrs-claus-netflix-hello-sunshine-1235875298%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeadline%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week%20that%2