-law%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20cruise%20continued%20sailing%2C%20and%20the%20tour%20company%20said%20they%20left%20her%20with%20other%20stranded%20cruisers.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20family%20said%20Norwegian%20failed%20to%20contact%20them%20while%20Lenkoff%20was%20abroad.%20They%20used%20an%20AirTag%20to%20track%20her%20journey%20home.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20a%20surprise%20to%20Julie%20Lenkoff's%20family%20that%20she%20was%20going%20on%20another%20cruise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2080-year-old%20has%20visited%20120%20countries%2C%20speaks%2010%20languages%2C%20and%20has%20been%20on%20countless%20cruises.%20Lenkoff%20is%20an%20experienced%20traveler%2C%20so%20no%20one%20batted%20an%20eye%20when%20she%20boarded%20a%2021-day%20Norwegian%20cruise%20along%20the%20coast%20of%20Africa%20by%20herself%20on%20March%2020%2C%20Kurt%20Gies%2C%20Lenkoff's%20son-in-law%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20family%20was%20shocked%20when%20another%20cruise%20passenger%20phoned%20Lenkoff's%20daughter%2C%20Lana%20Gies%2C%20to%20tell%20her%20they%20were%20with%20Lenkoff%2C%20Kurt%20said.%20She%20had%20been%20released%20from%20a%20hospital%2C%20could%20hardly%20speak%2C%20was%20losing%20her%20vision%2C%20and%20was%20on%20the%20African%20island%20of%20S%C3%A3o%20Tom%C3%A9%20and%20Pr%C3%ADncipe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKurt%20told%20BI%20Lenkoff%20had%20a%20stroke%20during%20a%20cruise-sponsored%20excursion%20and%20that%20the%20tour%20operator%20and%20cruise%20company%20left%20her%20at%20a%20hospital%2C%20where%20she%20was%20later%20discharged%20and%20left%20to%20figure%20out%20her%20own%20way%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKurt%20said%20a%20group%20of%20stranded%20tourists%20helped%20Lenkoff%20return%20to%20the%20US%2C%20where%20she%20remains%20in%20serious%20condition%20at%20the%20Stanford%20Medical%20Center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20the%20means%2C%20the%20technology%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20navigate%20this%20massive%20network%20to%20get%20her%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Kurt%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20only%20imagine%20if%20a%20family%20didn't%20or%20if%20that%20person%20was%20truly%20by%20themselves.%20What%20would've%20happened%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Julie%20Lenkoff%20on%20her%20cruise%20of%20Africa%20with%20Norweigan%20Cruise%20Lines.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660dc10716bde8d4ead56f70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJulie%20Lenkoff%20on%20a%20cruise-sponsored%20tour.%3Cp%3EJulie%20Lenkoff%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20family%20says%20they%20have%20other%20stranded%20cruisers%20to%20thank%20for%20Lenkoff's%20return%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2027%2C%20day%20eight%20of%20the%20Norwegian%20cruise%2C%20passengers%20disembarked%20the%20ship%20to%20explore%20S%C3%A3o%20Tom%C3%A9%20and%20Pr%C3%ADncipe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKurt%20said%20Lenkoff%20joined%20a%20cruise-sponsored%20excursion%20with%20the%20tour%20company%20Navetur%20Equatour.%20During%20the%20tour%2C%20she%20passed%20out%20and%20fell%2C%20Diogo%20Beir%C3%A3o%2C%20the%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20the%20tour%20company%2C%20confirmed%20to%20BI.%20When%20Lenkoff%20regained%20consciousness%2C%20he%20said%20she%20couldn't%20speak%20English%20and%20had%20lost%20feeling%20in%20the%20right%20side%20of%20her%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Beir%C3%A3o%20said%20the%20main%20concern%20was%20if%20Lenkoff%20had%20broken%20a%20bone%20or%20experienced%20a%20concussion.%20Kurt%20said%20doctors%20in%20the%20US%20later%20confirmed%20that%20Lenkoff%20had%20a%20stroke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeir%C3%A3o%20told%20BI%20that%20his%20tour%20guides%20brought%20Lenkoff%20back%20to%20the%20dock%2C%20where%20he%20says%20a%20nurse%20from%20the%20Norwegian%20cruise%20evaluated%20her%20on%20the%20pier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20sent%20to%20BI%2C%20a%20Norwegian%20cruise%20representative%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bon%20March%2027%2C%202024%2C%20an%2080-year-old%20woman%20was%20medically%20disembarked%20after%20being%20evaluated%20by%20our%20onboard%20medical%20team%2C%20who%20thought%20it%20best%20that%20she%20receive%20further%20assessment%20and%20treatment%20as%20needed%20from%20a%20local%20hospital.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeir%C3%A3o%20said%20Lenkoff%20was%20transported%20to%20the%20closest%20hospital%2C%20which%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20very%20comfortable%26quot%3B%20because%20it%20%26quot%3Bhad%20no%20private%20rooms%2C%20just%20curtains.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20Beir%C3%A3o%20said%20he%20believes%20it%20was%20the%20right%20decision%20not%20to%20let%20her%20reboard%20the%20cruise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKurt%20said%20Norwegian%20brought%20Lenkoff%20the%20belongings%20from%20her%20room%3B%20however%2C%20her%20credit%20cards%20and%20cash%20were%20lost.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20tour%20company%20later%20found%20the%20missing%20wallet%20in%20a%20tour%20van%2C%20which%20was%20brought%20to%20Lenkoff%20more%20than%2024%20hours%20after%20she%20was%20released%20from%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKurt%20said%20he%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20Lenkoff's%20family%20had%20no%20idea%20this%20was%20happening%20since%20Norwegian%20hadn't%20contacted%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Julie%20Lenkoff%20on%20a%20Norweigan%20cruise%20ship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660dc0f73f923f7dab046316%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJulie%20Lenkoff%20on%20a%20Norweigan%20cruise%20ship%3Cp%3EJulie%20Lenkoff%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20group%20of%20eight%20people%20were%20on%20a%20separate%2C%20private%20tour%20of%20S%C3%A3o%20Tom%C3%A9%20and%20Pr%C3%ADncipe.%20BI%20previously%20reported%20that%20the%20tour%20ran%20into%20issues%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-norwegian-cruise-stranded-them-on-african-island-over-missed-deadline-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20group%20missed%20the%20ship's%20boarding%20deadline%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20was%20stranded%20on%20the%20island%20without%20cash%20or%20medications%20and%20with%20one%20working%20credit%20card%2C%20which%20passengers%20Jill%20and%20Jay%20Campbell%20owned.%20The%20group%20found%20a%20hotel%2C%20contacted%20the%20closest%20American%20consulate%2C%20and%20planned%20to%20meet%20the%20ship%20at%20its%20next%20port%20in%20the%20Gambia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20all%20this%20was%20happening%2C%20Kurt%20said%2C%20Lenkoff%20was%20released%20from%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeir%C3%A3o%20said%20he%20was%20unaware%20that%20Lenkoff%20had%20a%20stroke%2C%20but%20he%20visited%20her%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bshe%20was%20not%20totally%20functional%26quot%3B%20but%20%26quot%3Bcould%20speak%20very%20well.%26quot%3B%20While%20Lenkoff%20could%20communicate%2C%20Beir%C3%A3o%20said%20she%20often%20forgot%20what%20she%20was%20trying%20to%20say%20mid-sentence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Norwegian's%20statement%2C%20the%20representative%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20attempted%20to%20call%20the%20guest%20several%20times%2C%20and%20as%20we%20were%20unable%20to%20reach%20her%2C%20we%20worked%20directly%20with%20our%20port%20agent%20in%20S%C3%A3o%20Tom%C3%A9%20and%20Pr%C3%ADncipe%2C%20an%20African%20island%20nation%2C%20to%20receive%20updates%20about%20the%20guest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20instances%20such%20as%20these%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3Bas%20the%20guest%20was%20released%20from%20the%20hospital%20and%20in%20a%20coherent%20state%2C%20our%20protocol%20is%20to%20contact%20the%20guest%20directly%2C%20as%20we%20would%20not%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20share%20any%20medical%20details%20with%20anyone%20else%20without%20their%20expressed%20consent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKurt%20said%20there%20are%20no%20phone%20or%20WhatsApp%20records%20of%20Norwegian%20reaching%20out%20on%20her%20cellphone%2C%20and%20he%20believes%20that%20family%20members%20should've%20been%20contacted%20in%20this%20instance%20since%20the%20company%20could%20not%20reach%20Lenkoff%20to%20confirm%20she%20was%20in%20a%20coherent%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20discharged%2C%20Kurt%20said%20the%20tour%20company%20connected%20the%20Americans%20with%20Lenkoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20people%20figuring%20out%20how%20they're%20getting%20off%20this%20island%2C%20and%20they're%20given%20the%20responsibility%20to%20take%20care%20of%20an%2080-year-old%20woman%20who%20just%20had%20a%20stroke%2C%26quot%3B%20Kurt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Lenkoff%20had%20no%20way%20to%20pay%20for%20anything%2C%20so%20the%20Campbells%20provided%20Lenkoff%20with%20food%20and%20a%20place%20to%20sleep%2C%20Kurt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20truly%20believe%20sometimes%20we're%20put%20in%20certain%20places%20for%20a%20reason%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20we%20were%20put%20in%20this%20place%20for%20the%2080-year-old%20woman%20who%20was%20left%20alone.%20God%20forbid%20what%20would%20have%20happened%20to%20that%20lady%20if%20we%20were%20not%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Jay%20Campbell%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wral.com%2Fstory%2Fsouth-carolina-couple-stranded-in-africa-cruise-ship-left-without-them%2F21357016%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENorth%20Carolina's%20WRAL%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKurt%20said%20Lenkoff%20was%20still%20having%20trouble%20speaking%20and%20had%20started%20to%20lose%20her%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20Lenkoff's%20phone%2C%20Jill%20Campbell%20called%20Lenkoff's%20daughter%20to%20tell%20her%20what%20happened.%20Around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20American%20consulate%20called%2C%20though%20Kurt%20said%20the%20family%20was%20unsure%20how%20the%20consulate%20learned%20about%20Lenkoff's%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKurt%20said%20he%20and%20Lana%20attempted%20to%20reach%20Norwegian%20multiple%20times%20but%20couldn't%20connect%20with%20anyone%20at%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20decided%20that%20we%20need%20to%20get%20Julie%20off%20that%20island%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20at%20Norwegian%20was%20going%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Norwegian%20representative%20told%20BI%20Lenkoff%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bescorted%20on%20a%20flight%20to%20Lisbon%2C%20Portugal%2C%20and%20then%20put%20in%20the%20care%20of%20airport%20staff%20to%20continue%20her%20journey%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20where%20she%20has%20now%20made%20a%20safe%20return.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKurt%20said%20all%20of%20Lenkoff's%20travel%20arrangements%20were%20%26quot%3Bmade%20by%20her%20family%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20wasn't%20Norwegian%20who%20escorted%20her%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bairlines%20took%20responsibility%20for%20ensuring%20she%20got%20safely%20on%20each%20plane%20segment%20during%20her%20journey%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Lenkoff%20flew%20to%20Lisbon%2C%20then%20to%20Toronto%2C%20and%20finally%20to%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20he%20said%2C%20Lana%20had%20sent%20her%20mom%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcruise-packing-list-airtag-apple-bag-traveler-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%20an%20Apple%20AirTag%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20the%20family%20could%20watch%20Lenkoff%20make%20the%20trip%20back%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Apple%20product%20has%20become%20popular%20for%20tracking%20everything%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funited-airlines-passenger-airtag-apple-lost-luggage-travel-flight-chaos-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emissing%20suitcases%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-airtag-track-lost-luggage-golfing-gear-flying-ireland-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elost%20golfing%20equipment%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewark-lost-bag-magician-bought-new-ticket-found-apple-airtag-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emagician's%20sound%20equipment%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20parents%20are%20even%20using%20them%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-parents-using-airtags-track-kids-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekeep%20track%20of%20their%20children%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Fapple-airtags-bluetooth-trackers-officially-175911565.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBenzinga%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Apple%20sold%20%241%20billion%20worth%20of%20Airtags%20within%20two%20years%20of%20releasing%20the%20tracking%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKurt%20said%20he%20and%20Lana%20used%20the%20AirTag%20to%20follow%20Lenkoff%20in%20Lisbon%20as%20she%20reached%20her%20next%20gate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20able%20to%20track%20her%20movement%20across%20the%20world%20as%20she%20was%20coming%20home%2C%20and%20that%20was%20a%20huge%20relief%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20Lenkoff%20arrived%20in%20California%2C%20Kurt%20said%20she%20was%20medically%20evacuated%20to%20the%20Stanford%20Medical%20Center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20pull%20her%20out%20on%20a%20gurney%20and%20this%20huge%20smile%20comes%20across%20her%20face%20as%20she%20sees%20her%20daughter%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Julie%20Lenkoff%20and%20her%20daughter%20Lana%20Gies.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660dc04316bde8d4ead56e78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJulie%20Lenkoff%20and%20her%20daughter%20Lana%20Gies.%3Cp%3EKurt%20Gies%3C%2Fp%3E%3C