%2C%20and%20stresses%20kind%20of%20moving%20around%20in%20the%20Earth's%20crust%2C%20every%20now%20and%20then%20one%20of%20those%20faults%20will%20become%20infrequently%20or%20intermittently%20active%2C%20just%20in%20a%20single%20earthquake%2C%20or%20a%20series%20of%20small%20earthquakes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20scientists%20know%2C%20those%20faults%20haven't%20been%20active%20since%20they%20formed%20%26quot%3Ba%20couple%20100%20million%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20ago%20Jobe%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20this%20is%20just%20one%20quake%20or%20a%20series.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feast-coast-prepare-earthquake-aftershocks-usgs-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAftershocks%20are%20possible%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20USGS%20warned.%20Most%20likely%20any%20aftershocks%20will%20be%20smaller%20quakes%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20small%20chance%20that%20an%20ensuing%20quake%20will%20be%20of%20similar%20or%20larger%20magnitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20there%20are%20dozens%20of%20faults%20in%20the%20Appalachian%20fold-and-thrust%20belt%2C%20USGS%20isn't%20yet%20able%20to%20attribute%20Friday's%20quake%20to%20any%20specific%20fault%20line%2C%20though%20early%20data%20suggests%20the%20culprit%20was%20about%203%20miles%20deep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20question%20is%20what%20caused%20the%20fault%20to%20reactivate%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThis%20quake%20may%20be%20a%20remnant%20of%20the%20Ice-Age%20glaciers'%20retreat%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20West%20Coast%2C%20earthquakes%20often%20come%20from%20movement%20along%20the%20boundaries%20of%20tectonic%20plates.%20The%20East%20Coast%2C%20however%2C%20is%20located%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20plate%20and%20doesn't%20experience%20much%20of%20that%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22tectonic%20plates%20noaa%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.in