ault%20lines%2C%20he%20said%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bgiven%20enough%20time%2C%20you%20can%20still%20build%20enough%20stress%20to%20cause%20the%20earthquakes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScientists%20should%20be%20able%20to%20discern%20whether%20glacial%20rebound%20contributed%20to%20Friday's%20tremor%20as%20they%20continue%20to%20analyze%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feast-coast-earthquake-came-from-ancient-sleeping-fault-reactivated-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712352566000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6610612116bde8d4ead645ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feast-coast-earthquake-came-from-ancient-sleeping-fault-reactivated-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20New%20Jersey%20earthquake%20came%20from%20ancient%20fault%20lines%20from%20the%20formation%20of%20North%20America%2C%20possibly%20triggered%20by%20stress%20from%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Ice%20Age.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mmcfalljohnsen%40businessinsider.com%20(Morgan%20McFall-Johnsen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A196%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feast-coast-earthquake-came-from-ancient-sleeping-fault-reactivated-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20says%20Tesla%20will%20unveil%20its%20robotaxi%20this%20year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20Tesla%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6582c21b1c5c7b8c9a0a2434%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk.%3Cp%3EODD%20ANDERSEN%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETesla%20will%20reveal%20its%20robotaxi%20in%20August%2C%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20EV-ma