%3Cp%3EDavid%20Berding%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20she%20really%20did%20that%20this%20past%20summer%2C%20and%20realized%20that%20%3Cem%3Ethat's%3C%2Fem%3E%20what's%20gonna%20take%20her%20game%20to%20the%20next%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20Alexander%20said%20as%20the%202023%20season%20came%20to%20a%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20few%20months%2C%20Clark%20put%20on%208%20pounds%20of%20muscle.%20Alexander%2C%20who%20also%20works%20with%20Iowa's%20women's%20gymnastics%20team%2C%20said%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20surprising%26quot%3B%20about%20her%20regimen.%20Sprints%2C%20squats%2C%20jumps%2C%20dead%20lifts%2C%20lunges%2C%20single-leg%20work%2C%20and%20ankle%20stability%20exercises%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Ball%20the%20normal%20things%20that%20people%20do%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20helped%20get%20her%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20sounds%20all%20well%20and%20good%20until%20you%20see%20her%20training.%20This%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCoachHuelle%2Fstatus%2F1685669570760056832%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20Clark%20taking%20300%20shots%20%E2%80%94%20mid-range%2C%203-point%2C%20and%20free-throw%20%E2%80%94%20in%20quick%20succession.%20Alexander%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F04%2F05%2Fwell%2Flive%2Fcaitlin-clark-iowa-training.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20saw%20that%20video%20and%20told%20Clark%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20you%20were%20running%20fast%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20days%20are%20more%20intense%20than%20others%2C%20and%20while%20Alexander%20%26quot%3Bcan't%20prevent%20injuries%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20takes%20painstaking%20care%20to%20help%20players%20avoid%20and%20mitigate%20them.%20She%20and%20the%20staff%20around%20her%20are%20able%20to%20monitor%20players'%20fatigue%20levels