0Lisa%20Bluder%2C%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20really%20the%20key%20to%20success%2C%20as%20far%20as%20basketball%20coaches%20and%20myself%2C%20is%20that%20we're%20working%20with%20the%20same%20athlete%20and%20we%20gotta%20make%20sure%20that%20we're%20sequencing%20everything%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Alexander%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20really%20the%20important%20part.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20piece%20of%20the%20puzzle%20for%20Clark%20or%20any%20other%20player%2C%20Alexander%20said%2C%20is%20their%20commitment%20to%20doing%20their%20%26quot%3Bbest%20every%20single%20day.%26quot%3B%20That's%20in%20the%20weight%20room%2C%20yes%2C%20but%20also%20in%20the%20moments%20when%20no%20one's%20watching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222276%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Caitlin%20Clark.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61ef0f5f702f4b001866c426%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClark%20high%20fives%20her%20Iowa%20Hawkeyes%20teammates.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FRonald%20Cortes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20have%20the%20best%20training%20and%20the%20best%20basketball%20coach%20and%20all%20these%20things%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20not%20sleeping%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20your%20body%20appropriately%2C%20then%20it%20doesn't%20really%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20Alexander%20said.%20%26quot%3B%5BClark%5D%20takes%20ownership%20of%20her%20sleep%20and%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20she's%20still%20a%20college%20kid%2C%20but%20good%20sleep%20and%20pretty%20good%20on%20the%20nutrition%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20has%20helped%20her%20really%20get%20to%20see%20the%20success%20from%20her%20training%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20she's%20doing%20the%20other%20things%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EExtra%20weight%20has%20helped%20Clark%20on%20the%20court%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202021-2022%20season%2C%20as