2C%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Haryana%20are%20extremely%20dependent%20on%20these%20outside%20inputs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeelam%20further%20points%20out%20that%2C%20unlike%20heirloom%20varieties%2C%20the%20seed%20saved%20from%20hybrids%20does%20not%20grow%20true%20to%20its%20type%20in%20the%20next%20cycle.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20will%20be%20less%20vigorous%20and%20more%20genetically%20variable.%20If%20you%20cannot%20replicate%20it%2C%20there%20is%20no%20point%20in%20keeping%20the%20seeds.%20It%20only%20compels%20farmers%20to%20buy%20new%20seeds%20every%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMeanwhile%2C%20heirloom%20seeds%20are%20genetically%20diverse%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20chemical-laden%20fertilisers%2C%20and%20are%20naturally%20resistant%20to%20disease%20and%20pests.%20As%20they%20are%20open-pollinated%2C%20you%20can%20easily%20replicate%20those%20seeds%20next%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20an%20example%20of%20how%20the%20produce%20harvested%20from%20both%20varieties%20differ%2C%20Neelam%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20tomatoes%20are%20available%20year-round%2C%20unlike%20in%20the%20past%20when%20we%20only%20had%20them%20in%20winter.%20To%20satisfy%20demand%2C%20farmers%20now%20grow%20tomatoes%20in%20mountainous%20areas%20with%20heavy%20fertiliser%20use.%20However%2C%20organically%20grown%20tomatoes%20in%20their%20respective%20seasons%20may%20not%20last%20as%20long%20but%20are%20richer%20in%20nutrients%2C%20tastier%2C%20and%20more%20vibrant%20in%20colour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20France%2C%20various%20tomato%20varieties%20were%20once%20used%20in%20different%20recipes%2C%20but%20now%20a%20single%2C%20sweeter%20tomato%20is%20used%20universally%2C%20replacing%20the%20sour%20ones%20of%20the%20past.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20120