%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eensure%20a%20good%20crop%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20benefitted%20him%20as%20well%20as%20the%20consumers%20%E2%80%94%20was%20to%20go%20back%20to%20his%20grandparents%E2%80%99%20style%20of%20farming%20and%20abandon%20chemicals%20and%20pesticides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Namakkal%20resident%20soon%20realised%20the%20benefits%20of%20organic%20farming%2C%20and%20through%20different%20training%20at%20the%20local%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%20(KVK)%2C%20along%20with%20his%20innovations%20and%20home%20recipes%20to%20keep%20pests%20at%20bay%2C%20Saravanan%20soon%20became%20a%20certified%20organic%20farmer%20with%20many%20awards%20up%20his%20sleeve.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20he%20has%20been%20practising%20integrated%20farming%20for%20several%20decades%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitiated%20with%20avoiding%20chemicals%20completely%2C%20he%20soon%20moved%20towards%20drip%20irrigation%2C%20vermicompost%2C%20a%20biogas%20unit%20and%20hydroponics.%20Unable%20to%20cultivate%20enough%20fodder%20for%20his%20cattle%2C%20hydroponic%20maize%20production%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20gamechanger%20for%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202018%2C%20he%20has%20been%20using%20this%20method%20to%20grow%20fodder%20for%20his%20livestock.%20What%E2%80%99s%20unique%20about%20it%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20grows%20it%20in%20his%20cupboard!%20He%20uses%20the%20soilless%20hydroponic%20method%20to%20grow%20maize%20fodder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20in%202018%2C%20he%20received%20the%20Haldhar%20Organic%20farmer%20award%20from%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Agricultural%20Research%20along%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98Innovative%20farmer%20award%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20Central%20government%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20did%20a%20farmer%20practising%20traditional%20farming%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20move%20to%20organic%20methods%20and%20find%20success%20in%20them%3F%20Here%E2%80%99s%20his%20s