-grow-fodder-save-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaize%20fodder%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20a%20hydroponics%20unit%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWash%20and%20soak%20the%20grains%20for%2024%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETie%20the%20seeds%20in%20a%20gunny%20bag%20and%20keep%20it%20in%20water%20for%2024%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETransfer%20the%20sprouted%20seeds%20to%20a%20tray%20and%20spread%20it%20out.%20Keep%20it%20in%20the%20cupboard.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWater%20it%20once%20every%20three%20hours%2C%20either%20manually%20or%20using%20a%20sprinkler%20with%20a%20timer%20for%207%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20yield%20will%20be%20ready%20on%20the%208th%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3Cem%3EPicture%20credits%3A%20P%20Saravanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712147266000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan-min-1712145955.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D346387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22P%20Saravanan%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20uses%20hydroponics%20to%20grow%20maize%20fodder%20for%20his%20cattle.%20He%20has%20also%20found%20a%20way%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20pesticides%20and%20keep%20his%20produce%20healthy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346387%2Forganic-farmer-namakkal-tamil-nadu-hydroponics-maize-fodder-drip-irrigation-p-saravanan%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22REI%20Fired%20A%20Popular%20Manager%20For%20Not%20Immediately%20Reporting%20Union%20Chatter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20incident%20shows%20how%20aggressively%20the%20liberal-branded%20retailer%20is%20responding%20to%20union%20organizing%20--%20and%20how%20low-level%20managers%20are%20caught%20in%20the%20middle.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712077178