nterestingly%2C%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Mumbai%2C%20Priyanka%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20apartment%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20haven%20for%20many%20butterfly%20species.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAffectionately%20dubbed%20the%20%E2%80%98Butterfly%20Mom%E2%80%99%2C%20Priyanka%20has%20transformed%20her%20balcony%20into%20a%20paradise%2C%20all%20set%20up%20to%20attract%20these%20winged%20beauties.%20Picture%20this%3A%20lemon%20plants%2C%20lantana%2C%20Jamaican%20spike%2C%20curry%20leaves%2C%20meswak%2C%20ixora%2C%20patharchatta%20%E2%80%94%20all%20blooming%20and%20buzzing%20with%20life.%20These%20plants%20aren%E2%80%99t%20just%20for%20show%20%E2%80%93%20they%20provide%20the%20perfect%20spots%20for%20butterflies%20to%20lay%20their%20eggs%20and%20nectar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fbutterfly-1712053091.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20In%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20she%20claims%20to%20have%20nurtured%20over%205%2C000%20butterflies.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fbutterfly-1712053091.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fbutterfly-1712053091-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fbutterfly-1712053091-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fbutterfly-1712053091-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fbutterfly-1712053091-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346253%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20In%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20she%20claims%20to%20have%20nurtured%20over%205%2C000%20butterflies.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20believes%20that%20these%20tiny%20eggs%20often%20fall%20victim%20to%20destruction%20during%20routine%20weeding%20or%20mindless%20pruning.%20Once%20hatched%20into%20caterpillars%2C%20they%20voraciously%20feed%20on%20plants%20until%20they%20undergo%20metamorphosis%20into%20pupae%2C%20eventually%20emerging%20as%20beautiful%20butterflies.%20Before%20taking%20flight%20to%20seek%20out%20new%20habitats%2C%20they%20rest%20and%20stretch%20their%20wings%2C%20preparing%20for%20their%20journey%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20Varanasi%2C%20Priyanka%20never%20imagined%20working%20to%20protect%20biodiversity.%20However%2C%20when%20she%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%2C%20she%20was%20disheartened%20to%20witness%20garbage%20and%20waste%20issues%20with%20ecological%20degradation.%20Having%20spent%20her%20childhood%20enjoying%20the%20shade%20of%20trees%20and%20rich%20biodiversity%2C%20she%20wanted%20to%20raise%20her%20daughter%20in%20an%20environment%20closer%20to%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20motivated%20her%20to%20create%20an%20urban%20organic%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20one%20day%2C%20she%20saw%20a%20small%20caterpillar%20eating%20a%20leaf%20from%20one%20of%20her%20plants.%20And%20after%20a%20few%20days%2C%20she%20saw%20that%20this%20caterpillar%20had%20transformed%20into%20a%20beautiful%20butterfly.%20After%20that%20incident%2C%20she%20became%20so%20fond%20of%20butterflies%20that%20she%20started%20reading%20about%20them.%20This%20newfound%20passion%20led%20her%20to%20create%20a%20small%20ecosystem%20within%20her%20high-rise%20apartment%2C%20where%20she%20rears%20butterflies%20on%20the%2013th%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20Priyanka%20claims%20to%20have%20nurtured%20over%205%2C000%20butterflies%20%E2%80%94%20including%20tailed%20jay%2C%20lime%20swallowtail%2C%20common%20mormon%2C%20red%20pierrot%2C%20blue%20tiger%2C%20salmon%20arab%2C%20and%20lime%20blue.%20She%20adds%20that%20rare%20species%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20the%20apefly%20butterfly%20and%20sunbeam%20butterfly%20%E2%80%94%20visit%20to%20lay%20their%20eggs%2C%20while%20others%20like%20the%20painted%20lady%2C%20common%20grass%20butterfly%2C%20common%20emigrant%2C%20common%20leopard%20butterfly%2C%20palm%20bob%2C%20and%20blank%20swift%20frequent%20the%20space%20for%20nectaring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fgreen-hope-1712213006.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Butterflies%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fgreen-hope-1712213006.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fgreen-hope-1712213006-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fgreen-hope-1712213006-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fgreen-hope-1712213006-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fgreen-hope-1712213006-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346472%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPriyanka%20rears%20butterflies%20on%20her%2013th-floor%20apartment%20balcony.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20that%2C%20she%20has%20been%20studying%20and%20documenting%20butterflies%20in%20her%20residential%20area%2C%20having%20successfully%20raised%20over%2055%20species%20from%20caterpillars.%20Among%20these%20are%20the%20common%20crow%2C%20plain%20tiger%2C%20blue%20tiger%2C%20blue%20moon%20or%20great%20eggfly%2C%20danaid%20eggfly%2C%20common%20jay%2C%20palm%20fly%2C%20giant%20red%20eye%2C%20common%20awl%2C%20peacock%20pansy%2C%20chocolate%20pansy%2C%20and%20lemon%20pansy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20claims%20