ng%20availability%2C%20chances%20of%20fading%20and%20cost.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20also%20an%20issue%20of%20colour%20consistency.%20The%20textile%20industry%20needs%20the%20colour%20to%20be%20of%20the%20same%20consistency%20on%20every%20cloth%20which%20becomes%20difficult%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F308824%2Fsustainable-fashion-brand-hibiscus-heroes-in-auroville-collection-includes-plant-dyed-fabrics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflower-derived%20colours%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20Vaishali%20Kulkarni%20of%20KBCols%20Sciences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKBCols%20is%20a%20science%20company%20that%20makes%20natural%20dyes.%20Co-founded%20by%20Vaishali%20Kulkarni%20and%20her%20husband%20Arjun%20Singh%2C%20the%20company%20has%20figured%20out%20a%20way%20of%20making%20natural%20dyes%20from%20waste%20by%20using%20microbes!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20does%20the%20science%20behind%20this%20work%3F%20The%20founders%20explain%20the%20intricacies%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98This%20was%20destiny%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Vaishali%20informs%20she%20never%20planned%20that%20she%20would%20become%20an%20entrepreneur.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20science%20person%20but%20the%20turn%20of%20events%20led%20me%20into%20the%20colour%20industry%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20her%20postgraduate%20studies%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20opt%20for%20a%20PhD%20from%20a%20college%20in%20Mumbai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20PhD%20studies%2C%20projects%20often%20came%20to%20our%20college%20concerning%20the%20treatment%20of%20coloured%20water%20in%20the%20textile%20department.%20Researchers%20were%20tasked%20with%20addressing%20this%20issue%20by%2