r%20guests.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-10-1711117348.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-10-1711117348-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-10-1711117348-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-10-1711117348-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-10-1711117348-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345626%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20retreat%20offers%20global%20cuisines%20to%20their%20guests.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20has%20already%20tried%20to%20incorporate%20the%20culture%20of%20the%20area%20into%20their%20homestay.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20Kumaoni%20art%20hung%20in%20the%20place%20to%20give%20the%20guests%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20culture.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIte%20brought%20handlooms%20and%20pieces%20of%20art%20from%20Kashmir%20to%20make%20the%20place%20a%20hub%20of%20different%20cultures%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20place%20was%20our%20stepping%20stone%20to%20return%20home%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20place%20feels%20like%20one%20to%20us.%20Including%20elements%20of%20both%20our%20cultures%20and%20the%20design%20of%20the%20place%20we%20called%20home%20for%20so%20long%20in%20Switzerland%20was%20quite%20important%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussing%20various%20activities%20that%20they%20provide%2C%20Ite%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20about%20three%20trekking%20routes%20that%20we%20encourage%20our%20guests%20to%20take.%20We%20also%20recommend%20exploring%20the%20area%20and%20exploring%20the%20Bhowali%20range.%20The%20guests%20can%20also%20engage%20in%20bird%20watching%20as%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F175950%2Findia-padma-shri-anup-sah-photography-himalayas-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20place%20is%20full%20of%20Himalayan%3C%2Fa%3E%20birds%20visiting%20the%20estate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20150%20species%20of%20birds%20are%20found%20in%20the%20area%2C%20she%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20have%20lots%20of%20books%20for%20children%20to%20engage%20in%20reading%2C%20and%20a%20bonfire%20and%20barbeque%20for%20the%20guests.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20the%20place%20is%20perfect%20for%20stargazing.%20The%20skies%20on%20a%20clear%20night%20are%20full%20of%20beautiful%20stars%20that%20our%20guests%20can%20enjoy%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Varun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20attraction%20of%20the%20place%20is%20its%20delicious%20food.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20the%20guests%20to%20experience%20every%20cuisine%20they%20want%20when%20they%20visit%20Himalaica.%20So%20we%20hired%20chefs%20who%20can%20cook%20anything%20you%20want%20at%20your%20command%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Varun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSay%20you%20want%20to%20eat%20something%20from%20Italian%20cuisine%20or%20French%20cuisine%2C%20you%20can%20ask%20the%20chefs%20to%20cook%20those%20dishes%20for%20you.%20We%20also%20offer%20classes%20if%20the%20guests%20want%20to%20learn%20to%20cook%20any%20particular%20dish%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20has%20hosted%20countless%20guests%20at%20the%20property%20so%20far.%20The%20common%20review%20that%20the%20couple%20gets%20from%20their%20guests%20is%20how%20the%20property%20feels%20like%20home%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCZjivJ3MfCo%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloadi