rown%20from%20a%2010%C3%9710%20square%20feet%20room%20to%20a%20business%20that%2C%20this%20financial%20year%2C%20is%20slated%20to%20generate%20revenues%20of%20about%20(USD)%20%242%20million%20(approx%20Rs%2016.6%20crore)%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20imperative%20to%20gauge%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20the%20Sankethi%20people%20and%20their%20cuisine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20January%202011%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20C%20N%20Ramachandran%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Sanketi%20%5BSankethi%5D%20community%20is%20a%20small%20sub-sect%20of%20%3Cem%3ESmartha%20Brahmins%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20about%2025%2C000%20people%20who%20migrated%20from%20Southern%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20a%20few%20centuries%20ago.%20They%20are%20found%20mostly%20in%20old%20Mysuru%20state%20(especially%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%20of%20Kaveri%20and%20Tunga%20rivers)%2C%20and%2C%20traditionally%2C%20they%20are%20noted%20for%20agriculture%2C%20study%20of%20the%20Vedas%2C%20and%20classical%20music.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20speak%20a%20dialect%20which%20has%20freely%20borrowed%20words%20and%20grammatical%20structures%20from%20Kannada%2C%20Malayalam%2C%20and%20Tulu%2C%20besides%20retaining%20certain%20Tamil%20elements%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Ramachandran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPulyogare-Ambode-Majjigehuli--1710945717.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Puliyogare%20(tamarind%20rice)%2C%20ambode%20(a%20type%20of%20vada)%2C%20and%20majjige%20huli%20(yogurt%20and%20vegetable-based%20curry).%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPulyogare-Ambode-Majjigehuli--1710945717.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPulyogare-Ambode-Majjigehuli--1710945717-300x157.